                    <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
                    <h3>Our Story</h3>
                    <p style="width: 500px">Welcome to Expense Tracker, your go-to solution for managing your personal or business finances. Our mission is to provide you with a user-friendly and efficient tool to track your expenses, simplify your budgeting process, and help you achieve your financial goals.At Expense Tracker, we understand the importance of keeping track of your expenses and staying on top of your finances. Our platform allows you to easily categorize your expenses, set budgets, and monitor your spending in real-time. With our intuitive interface, you can quickly see where your money is going and identify areas where you can cut back and save.</p>
                    <p style="width: 500px">Expense tracker was developed by  group of 5 people Aslesh Gattargi,Karvika Kushwaha,Lavanya Thanneeru,Shreyaa Dayananda and Syed Mateen under the guidance of our trainer Ramesh Kumar Sir.It employs the use of ASP.NET MVC application.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
